{"type":null,"faqId":13106,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02  连接WLAN 成功后经常自动断开，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">成功后，请保持在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若在有效距离内仍然会出现自动断开的情况，可能是由于手机与提供热点的路由器不兼容。请重启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开关或重启路由器。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置界面，点击</span><span>&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">高级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，然后点击<b>在休眠状态下保持</b></span><b><span> WLAN </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，打开选项菜单，选择<b>始终</b>。手机将始终保持与</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络的连接。<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37743\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":3,"unUseful":11,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4070","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1402018586000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":1129,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":15,"times":5,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}